summary: first in a series of home mods
descriptionHtml:
Adds a tower home in the Falkeath hold by the lake.
Has  Cooking, Alchemy and Enchanting in the tower, while the Tanning Rack, Workbench
and Grindwheel are on a deck, and the Forge Chopping block and Smelter are near the bottom
of the stairs leading to the tower entrance. Has severel non- respawning containers.

UPDATE-
Added 4 specific storage containers for crafting stations.
author: Jacob
